		"description": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a6ea03e8-7fff-cef4-10b1-8f49d5142a17\">All Lovesworn hold similar tenets, regardless of the object of their devotion.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a6ea03e8-7fff-cef4-10b1-8f49d5142a17\"><strong>As You Wish.</strong> No task is too great, nor too small, in the service of those you love.</span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a6ea03e8-7fff-cef4-10b1-8f49d5142a17\"><strong>Ever Faithful.</strong> Within the bounds of your conscience, you never break trust with a loved one.<br><strong>Selfless.</strong> You always prefer the good of those you love, even at your own expense.</span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a6ea03e8-7fff-cef4-10b1-8f49d5142a17\"><strong>Thick and Thin.</strong> You share in both the bounties and the sufferings of those you love.</span></li>\n</ul>",
